{"tid":1453774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"商台 903 全日改播特備節目「還我們公義」　邀聽眾向政府、警方提問","createTime":"2019-08-12T05:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T05:59:33.000Z","uid":19552,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2846459e5ee97fc0b15772f83842446103538051","tid":1453774,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:18:11.000Z","msg":"昨日（8月11日）警方在全港多區武力清場，期間有警員疑喬裝示威者、在港鐵站內施放催淚彈、近距離掃射人群等，手法備受爭議。商業電台 903 今日將作出特別安排，全日改播特備節目《還我們公義 903個個為什麼？》，歡迎聽眾向警方與政府作出提問。<br />\n<br />\n903 fb 專頁中午張貼名為《還我們公義 903個個為什麼？》的圖片，公布宣布電台節目安排，指因應社會狀況，903 今日由上午十點至深夜兩點所有節目，將會改為播放特備節目《還我們公義 903個個為什麼？》，「主持人會配合歌曲不停向警方與政府作出提問，歡迎聽眾一同參與一同發問，主持人會代大家發聲」。<br />\n<br />\n另外節目《早霸王》今早亦在 FB 發出呼籲，歡迎聽眾留言向政府及警方發問：「香港變成咁，相信廣大香港市民，都有唔少問題想問政府，想問警方，歡迎喺下面留言，我哋會喺大氣電波發問。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/p526x296/67900617_10156968717733558_3903986798023409664_n.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_oc=AQkyoYzMSDeNzZI_2NlSquiWHOMcoC5uhQWsBumsbyGeGX8IaIgk5ztGn8blzeHsmEI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=6d2fc1f830e7eafd39c383bc34bf49bd&amp;oe=5DDA658A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-0%2Fp526x296%2F67900617_10156968717733558_3903986798023409664_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_oc%3DAQkyoYzMSDeNzZI_2NlSquiWHOMcoC5uhQWsBumsbyGeGX8IaIgk5ztGn8blzeHsmEI%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D6d2fc1f830e7eafd39c383bc34bf49bd%26oe%3D5DDA658A&h=3fa4580a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40e0223f35ef8d509692af99c8394cc956dab191","tid":1453774,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d9ced1c799180129c5586ce790b8fca29c3ec3","tid":1453774,"uid":222238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:20:15.000Z","msg":"良心不會磨滅"},{"pid":"dc9c9e955ec7ff9b746a53d5bb3a25d8e24a082f","tid":1453774,"uid":284732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited